<h3>Radiation and Cloudiness</h3>
Due to the above-mentioned block pressure pattern over Europe (Figure 1) a rather unique pattern can be seen in the anomaly figures of radiation and cloud cover (Figures 14,15). Over central Europe an extreme positive radiation anomaly and negative cloud cover anomaly can be recognized.
